<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>889</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>bì xū yào zhòng shēng 迦南889</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 hěn duō hěn duō nián qián de yī gè shēn yè, yǒu yī gè rén lái qiú jiàn yé sū.
 nǐ yī dìng zhī dào tā shì shéi, tā de míng jiào ní gē dǐ mǔ.
 yé sū shí shí zài zài de gào sù tā, jìn rù shén de guó dù, bì xū yào zhòng shēng.
 bì xū yào zhòng shēng, bì xū yào zhòng shēng. shì cóng shuǐ hé shèng líng ér shēng.
 duō shǎo gè shēn yè yǐ qiāo qiāo guò qù, ní gē dǐ mǔ dōu zài chàng zhe zhè yī shǒu gē.
 bì xū yào zhòng shēng, bì xū yào zhòng shēng. nǐ bì xū yào zhòng shēng.</lyrics>
</song>